description: Throughout the past 2 years, we have heard the term “religious liberty” more than ever before. But when we, the Seventh-day Adventist Church, talk about Religious Liberty–what do we mean? How can we defend religious liberty–not just for our members, but for everyone. This week, Jennifer and Sam sit down with Orlan Johnson and Jennifer Woods to talk about why understanding religious liberty and its role is so important to Christians today.
tags: freedom to choose and practice religion
